Choose the level of guidancethat's right for you



Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCSelective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLC






What is it?


Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCAutomated investing with low-cost, low minimum investment, with access to five goal-oriented ETF portfolios.


Selective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCA broader range of goal-oriented portfolios made up of mutual funds and ETFs, based on varying investment objectives and risk with ongoing rebalancing and monitoring.





Who is this best for?


Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCDigital-savvy, long-term focused investors looking for a simple way to get low-cost, diversified portfolio recommendations. Our Financial Consultants can help you get started.


Selective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCDigital-savvy and long-term focused investors, looking for more sophisticated strategies and portfolio recommendations. Our Financial Consultants can help you choose which portfolio is right for you.





Managing and tracking


Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCDigital dashboard with advanced managing and tracking features and access to a Financial Consultant


Selective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLCDigital dashboard with advanced managing and tracking features and access to a Financial Consultant





Minimum investment


Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLC$5,000


Selective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLC$25,000





Advisory fees


Essential PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLC0.30%


Selective PortfoliosOffered through TD Ameritrade Investment Management, LLC0.75%-1.25% for the first $100,000 (varies by portfolio and investment amount)



